            <div type="transcript" id="F548A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Black Berry - wears<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 a Thorn in his side -</l>
                    <l>But no Man heard Him cry - </l>
                    <l>He offers His Berry, just<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the same </l>
                    <l>To Partridge - and to Boy - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>He sometimes holds opon the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Fence -</l>
                    <l>Or struggles to a Tree - </l>
                    <l>Or clasps a Rock, with<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 both His Hands - </l>
                    <l>But not for sympathy - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We - tell a Hurt - to cool it - </l>
                    <l>This Mourner - to the Sky</l>
                    <l>A little further reaches -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 instead - </l>
                    <l>Brave Black Berry - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
